      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TIME TO WORK (4) had the drop on the lead and went on to be beaten 5.5 lengths into second (23.85) at Casino in a Maiden over 411m. Expected to feature in the finish again. ROCKATANSKY (7) is a Denise Robinson-trained newcomer by Shima Shine out of Thurles Princess with no trial form to work with. Profiles nicely but market best guide to ability. TICK GIRL (1) was responsible for a modest effort most recently when seventh at this track over 352m behind Get Ahead Tina (20.24) in a Maiden. Placed at her previous run. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Has ability and can atone. OUR GIRL ANNA (3) is a newcomer from the Geoffrey Dwyer kennel. Can sneak into the frame at her first appearance.",
